{
  "texts": [
    "OrganizationThe rest of this survey is organized as follows.",
    "In Section 2, we first present a comprehensive overview of ISAC, covering various ISAC systems, fundamental tradeoffs, and diverse applications.",
    "Subsequently, Section 3 illustrates the key techniques involved in the three categories of ISAC systems.",
    "Section 4 offers an overview of various AI techniques, including ML, DL, DRL, FL, GAI, and TL, with the comparison between model-based methods and AI-based ones for ISAC in Section 5.",
    "Section 6 discusses the AI designs for ISAC and the recent trends for AI-enabled ISAC are provided in Section 7."
  ]
}